show.description: The president of Stewart Group dies mysteriously at home, leaving his daughter Florence blind. Determined to uncover the truth, she suspects her father's protector, Walt, might be the culprit. Through her investigation, she unravels the mystery and finds love. Watch "Don't Mess With the Blind Heiress" Now!
